      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 inline-six heritage. Featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, the powerplant delivers linear torque and a signature metallic rasp. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a structural reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points. The chassis retains its composure with a well-sorted suspension geometry, offering the communicative steering feel purists demand. While it shows the minor cosmetic patina expected of a well-loved driver, its mechanical vitals are robust and track-capable.",
